  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This multicentric prospective randomized controlled trial (RCT) compares the Leeds Pathology
      Protocol (LEEPP) with other &quot;conventional&quot; pathological protocol of PD specimen for
      periampullary cancer. Our aims were to evaluate the impact of the protocol and of the
      clearance on R1 rate and its prognostic value.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
